# Linguist configuration for GitHub
# ===========================

# --- Ignore build & generated artifacts ---
**/target/**                  linguist-vendored
**/logs/**                    linguist-generated
**/profile_report/**          linguist-generated
**/profile_report/analysis_html/**  linguist-generated
**/dbt_packages/**            linguist-vendored
**/dbt_internal_packages/**   linguist-vendored
**/.venv/**                   linguist-vendored

# --- Ignore temporary and system folders ---
**/__pycache__/**             linguist-generated
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/**      linguist-generated

# --- Detect and classify key source languages ---
# dbt SQL models and macros
**/*.sql                      linguist-language=SQL      linguist-detectable=true
# YAML configuration (dbt and project settings)
**/*.yml                      linguist-language=YAML     linguist-detectable=true
**/*.yaml                     linguist-language=YAML     linguist-detectable=true
# Python scripts (profiling, automation)
**/*.py                       linguist-language=Python   linguist-detectable=true
# JSON configuration files
**/*.json                     linguist-language=JSON     linguist-detectable=true

# --- Documentation and tests ---
**/docs/**                    linguist-documentation
**/tests/**                   linguist-detectable=true